rows.label: qst201616_0010
rows.name: Kiara-chan...

rows.label: qst201616_0020
rows.name: I did well...

rows.label: qst201616_0030
rows.name: Yes! It was really great!

rows.label: qst201616_0040
rows.name:
Your happy feeling was
passed on to us...

rows.label: qst201616_0050
rows.name:
Your song made everyone sparkle
and thrill with excitement...

rows.label: qst201616_0060
rows.name: It's all thanks to you, Kiara-chan...

rows.label: qst201616_0070
rows.name:
It all started when you
spoke to me that time...

rows.label: qst201616_0080
rows.name:
I played so much with the Torigonda
that Kiara-chan lent me.

rows.label: qst201616_0090
rows.name:
I promised when we first met that
I would return it someday...

rows.label: qst201616_0100
rows.name: I think that time is now...

rows.label: qst201616_0110
rows.name: No...

rows.label: qst201616_0120
rows.name: You should keep the Torigonda, miss.

rows.label: qst201616_0130
rows.name: I can have another one made for me...

rows.label: qst201616_0140
rows.name: You see... I'm graduating today.

rows.label: qst201616_0150
rows.name:
I intended for this to be
a one-time performance...

rows.label: qst201616_0160
rows.name: Mo-mooo!

rows.label: qst201616_0170
rows.name: Is that so...

rows.label: qst201616_0180
rows.name:
I want to have the courage to fight as a Blade... I
want to change myself to be useful to everyone...

rows.label: qst201616_0190
rows.name: That's why I started this...

rows.label: qst201616_0200
rows.name: On such a big stage...

rows.label: qst201616_0210
rows.name:
And with so many people
listening to my song...

rows.label: qst201616_0220
rows.name:
Now that I've gained confidence in
myself, I think it's time to graduate.

rows.label: qst201616_0230
rows.name: Mo-mo-mooo!

rows.label: qst201616_0240
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: qst201616_0250
rows.name:
It's a shame I won't be able
to hear you sing anymore...

rows.label: qst201616_0260
rows.name:
I'm sure everyone who came
here today will be sad too...

rows.label: qst201616_0270
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: qst201616_0280
rows.name: But it's your decision, miss.

rows.label: qst201616_0290
rows.name:
I look forward to seeing you
shine as a Blade from now on.

rows.label: qst201616_0300
rows.name: Yes... I'll do my best.

rows.label: qst201616_0310
rows.name:
I've had so much help from my Driver
and my producer until now...

rows.label: qst201616_0320
rows.name:
But from now on, I'll
be the one to help.

rows.label: qst201616_0330
rows.name: That's the spirit.

rows.label: qst201616_0340
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: qst201616_0360
rows.name: Thank you for everything...

rows.label: qst201616_0370
rows.name: You're welcome.
